        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 36,
            "y1": 317,
            "x2": 423,
            "y2": 408
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 4,
        "text": "तीर्थेषु पशुयज्ञेषु काष्ठपाषाणमृन्मये । प्रतिमायां मनो येषां ते नर:मूढ़चेतस:॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/sankaracarya1925_07_textline_4.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 40,
            "y1": 385,
            "x2": 1192,
            "y2": 472
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 5,
        "text": "अर्थ --- तीर्थों में और पशुओं के यज्ञों में और मट्टी-पत्थर की मूर्तियों",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/sankaracarya1925_07_textline_5.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 100,
            "y1": 452,
            "x2": 1178,
            "y2": 542
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 6,
        "text": "में जिन पुरुषों का मन लगता है, वह पुरुष अति मूढ़ कहे जाते हैं ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/sankaracarya1925_07_textline_6.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 38,
            "y1": 531,
            "x2": 1190,
            "y2": 614
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 7,
        "text": "कपिल-गीता ---",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/sankaracarya1925_07_textline_7.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 107,
            "y1": 622,
            "x2": 408,
            "y2": 702
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 8,
        "text": "कहाँ पर रहता है ?",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/sankaracarya1925_07_textline_8.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 48,
            "y1": 1116,
            "x2": 408,
            "y2": 1212
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 9,
        "text": "पाषाणैरालयं बद्ध्वा देव: पाषाण एव च ।",
